--Gaat het niet zoals het moet, dan moet het maar zoals het gaat.

217
00:32:03.845 --> 00:32:20.357
--If it doesn't go the way it should, then it should go the way it does. That's not desperation. That's pragmatism. The kind of pragmatism you develop when you've been shipping alone for eight years and the only person who can tell you it's good enough is you.

